OL,3,C'No quick fix,' to Lough Neagh crisis
OL,5,FStormont's environment minister has
OL,6,Fwarned there are no quick fixes for
OL,7,Fthe environment crisis in Lough Neagh
OL,8,Fsaying it is vital to start now on
OL,9,Ftackling it.
OL,11,FAndrew Muir made the comments while
OL,12,Fproviding an update on the Lough Neagh
OL,13,FReport and Action Plan, as well as
OL,14,Foutlining a number of measures to be
OL,15,Fundertaken by his department.
OL,17,FIn 2023, the UK's largest body of
OL,18,Ffresh water turned green due to
OL,19,Funprecedented levels of blue-green
OL,20,Falgae.
