OL,3,C'No quick fix,' to Lough Neagh crisis
OL,5,F"It's a long term project."
OL,7,FMr Muir said he brought the Lough
OL,8,FNeagh Report and Action Plan to the
OL,9,FExecutive a number of weeks ago.
OL,11,FIt contains 37 actions - some of which
OL,12,Fthe minister explained would require
OL,13,FExecutive approval as they "cut across
OL,14,Fdepartments".
OL,16,FOf those, 20 have been given the go-
OL,17,Fahead by the agriculture minister as
OL,18,Fthey fall within his department's
OL,19,Fremit.
