OL,3,C'No quick fix,' to Lough Neagh crisis
OL,5,FThe minister has allocated #6million
OL,6,Ftoward the actions. Around #2.8m of
OL,7,Fthat money is to go towards resource,
OL,8,Fincluding hiring additional staff
OL,9,F"with firm force on enforcement",
OL,10,Fwhile #3.2m is for capital investment.
OL,12,FThe actions contained within the draft
OL,13,Freport fall into four categories:
OL,15,FIn terms of ownership of Lough Neagh,
OL,16,FAndrew Muir told MLAs that he has
OL,17,Fsought "further meetings" with the
OL,18,FEarl of Shaftesbury.
